29:22.694 --> 29:26.865
But I sure know you can't
pray with kids in schools.

29:28.500 --> 29:30.010
- You ever try that?

29:30.034 --> 29:31.445
- Praying?

29:31.469 --> 29:32.469
Who hasn't?

29:34.706 --> 29:36.750
- What'd you ask for?

