- For what?

29:37.775 --> 29:38.986
- For what?

29:39.010 --> 29:41.288
- That I wouldn't have
a wife that cheated.

29:41.312 --> 29:42.623
- And?

29:42.647 --> 29:44.325
- I'm divorced.

29:44.349 --> 29:46.694
- Because she cheated?

29:46.718 --> 29:47.718
- No.

29:48.520 --> 29:49.520
- You did.

29:57.095 --> 29:59.664
- I don't think I can help you.

30:01.132 --> 30:04.178
- Counselor, what do
you want most in life?

30:04.202 --> 30:06.104
- Make money, be happy.

30:09.374 --> 30:11.476
- Well, all I want to do,

30:13.178 --> 30:14.279
is help kids.

30:15.413 --> 30:18.016
I want to help boys become men.

30:19.484 --> 30:21.795
To coach them and help them,
it's the only thing I know

30:21.819 --> 30:22.963
how to do.

30:22.987 --> 30:26.567
That's what I'm good
at, that's my calling

30:26.591 --> 30:28.026
is to do that and

30:29.427 --> 30:31.505
that's why I'm here right
now, is because a kid came

30:31.529 --> 30:33.031
to me for help and

30:34.532 --> 30:36.877
and I gave it to him,

30:36.901 --> 30:39.980
the best way I know how, the
only way I knew how to help him

30:40.004 --> 30:43.908
and they took everything
away from me for that.

30:47.579 --> 30:49.414
So I'm here now asking

30:50.315 --> 30:52.293
for your help,

30:52.317 --> 30:55.429
and yeah, you would be putting
your neck out on the line,

30:55.453 --> 30:58.132
but that's what I did for
somebody who needed help

30:58.156 --> 31:00.592
and that's why I'm here so...

31:07.065 --> 31:09.834
Come on, let's
make some history.

31:32.056 --> 31:33.734
- I need a retainer.

31:33.758 --> 31:36.637
Up front in case you
have a crisis of faith.

31:36.661 --> 31:39.039
I'll do the rest on contingency.

31:39.063 --> 31:40.999
- How much do you need?

31:42.267 --> 31:43.267
- $10,500.

31:45.003 --> 31:47.003
- Mr. Brown, I'm unemployed,
I don't have access to

31:47.027 --> 31:48.595
that kind of money.

31:50.508 --> 31:53.177
- I can't do it for free, swami.

32:02.153 --> 32:04.989
- Would you take $5000, Mr.
Brown?

32:37.188 --> 32:38.690
- Michael?

32:43.161 --> 32:44.872
- What are you doing here?

32:44.896 --> 32:46.607
How did you know where I was?

32:46.631 --> 32:49.634
- Do you realize
what you are doing?

32:50.935 --> 32:53.781
I just want to pay my score.

32:53.805 --> 32:55.616
They're gonna make me
tell them everything.

32:55.640 --> 32:57.141
Everything I know.

32:58.576 --> 33:00.421
You should check your office.

33:00.445 --> 33:01.555
- Why?

33:01.579 --> 33:04.058
- They left a message.

33:59.504 --> 34:01.849
- You know you give
a person a chance

34:01.873 --> 34:04.618
and they just take advantage
of you, today you just

34:04.642 --> 34:07.287
can't be nice, didn't want
to listen to the pretty face

34:07.311 --> 34:08.722
that you got involved,

34:08.746 --> 34:11.492
after you knew your
line was closed.

34:11.516 --> 34:13.393
I want my money.

34:13.418 --> 34:15.362
And whatever happens to
the people you love,

34:15.386 --> 34:16.621
that's all you.

34:34.205 --> 34:37.484
- We should go, get out of here.

34:37.507 --> 34:38.507
- Go?

34:39.210 --> 34:40.353
Go where?

34:40.378 --> 34:42.547
- Anywhere, just not here.

34:45.349 --> 34:46.583
A vacation, hm?

34:49.087 --> 34:51.206
I mean you spend all your
time around these old things

34:51.231 --> 34:52.299
nobody wants.

34:53.357 --> 34:55.636
- Oh, so I guess
I'm nobody, huh?

34:55.659 --> 34:58.038
- Well I didn't mean nobody.

34:58.062 --> 35:02.209
I just meant we should
be, more spontaneous.

35:02.233 --> 35:03.233
Leave.

35:03.935 --> 35:06.146
- I have to work.

35:06.170 --> 35:07.772
- You own the shop.

35:09.006 --> 35:11.509
- And I need $10,400 remember?

35:13.878 --> 35:14.979
- I remember.

35:16.247 --> 35:19.092
But a few days won't hurt.

35:19.116 --> 35:22.463
I mean the case is gonna
be settled real soon.

35:22.487 --> 35:23.487
- It will?

35:24.489 --> 35:25.489
- It will.

35:29.961 --> 35:32.506
- Michael look at me.

35:32.530 --> 35:35.576
In my eyes and tell me you
think this case is gonna

35:35.600 --> 35:36.934
be settled soon.

35:38.870 --> 35:39.870
- It will.

35:42.840 --> 35:44.585
- We're the same.

35:44.609 --> 35:46.010
Exactly same DNA.

35:49.157 --> 35:50.157
- It will.

35:50.181 --> 35:51.182
- Michael...

36:26.684 --> 36:27.995
- This is a...

36:28.019 --> 36:30.855
- I've known about
it for a while.

36:31.956 --> 36:34.635
I just wanted to see how
long it was gonna take

36:34.659 --> 36:36.994
for you to tell me about it.

36:42.043 --> 36:43.043
- Why didn't you...

36:43.067 --> 36:44.067
- Why?

36:48.940 --> 36:51.084
Because with people you love,

36:51.108 --> 36:53.611
you tend to be more forgiving.

36:55.346 --> 36:59.159
But I just kept hoping that
you would do something,

36:59.183 --> 37:01.595
do something to make it right.

37:01.619 --> 37:02.619
- Laurel...

37:10.194 --> 37:12.239
- And you want me to leave,

37:12.263 --> 37:13.273
my life.

37:13.297 --> 37:15.842
You look around here and

37:15.866 --> 37:19.112
you see old stuff,
but I see treasures.

37:19.136 --> 37:22.683
The people who made
all this stuff,

37:22.707 --> 37:26.253
they've long since passed,
but what they put their

37:26.277 --> 37:27.277
hands to

37:28.446 --> 37:29.447
is treasure.

37:31.782 --> 37:36.430
That's their legacy and I
used to have one of my own.

37:36.454 --> 37:40.124
That died in that car
accident, so right now.

37:41.292 --> 37:44.838
I just want to make
their legacy live on

37:44.862 --> 37:45.862
right here.

37:49.734 --> 37:52.336
So no, I don't need a vacation.

37:53.404 --> 37:55.406
I am where I need to be.

37:58.209 --> 38:00.320
- I'll pay you back.

38:00.344 --> 38:01.344
Every cent.

38:07.451 --> 38:08.886
- I have to work.

38:11.656 --> 38:13.991
- Laurel, I'll pay you back.

38:14.925 --> 38:15.925
I promise.

38:19.730 --> 38:20.730
I promise.

38:30.941 --> 38:31.941
- Oh God.

38:34.512 --> 38:37.324
- That's my sister, my heart.

38:37.348 --> 38:39.893
I did this to her,
I got to fix it.

38:39.917 --> 38:41.352
I'm gonna fix it.

38:42.753 --> 38:43.753
Watch me.

38:51.762 --> 38:53.006
- I pledge allegiance

38:53.030 --> 38:56.109
to the flag of the United
States of America,

38:56.133 --> 38:59.112
and to the republic
for which it stands

38:59.136 --> 39:03.383
one nation indivisible with
liberty and justice for all.

39:03.407 --> 39:04.742
Have a nice day.

39:05.776 --> 39:06.777
- Under God.

39:08.779 --> 39:10.114
- Do I know you?

39:11.582 --> 39:12.583
- Under God.

39:14.418 --> 39:16.596
One nation under God.

39:16.620 --> 39:19.633
Approved by Congress in 1954,

39:19.657 --> 39:23.828
is there a specific reason
you excluded that phrase?

39:27.431 --> 39:29.333
Oh, you've been served,

39:30.434 --> 39:32.913
by Michael Brown,
attorney at law.

39:32.937 --> 39:35.539
Mr. Paul will see you in court.

39:42.913 --> 39:45.158
- And the plaintiff should
be allowed a hearing

39:45.182 --> 39:47.027
for immediate reinstatement.

39:47.051 --> 39:49.930
My client's season will be
nearly over in 60 days,

39:49.954 --> 39:51.098
your Honor.

39:51.122 --> 39:53.433
- My client needs more
time for discovery.

39:53.457 --> 39:55.102
We need more time.

39:55.126 --> 39:56.803
Six months is what
we're thinking.

39:56.827 --> 39:58.138
- Six...

39:58.162 --> 40:01.208
Your Honor, this hearing
should take place this week.

40:01.232 --> 40:03.577
- That's not feasible and
besides that's absurd.

40:03.601 --> 40:05.112
- That is not absurd...

40:05.136 --> 40:07.147
- I have heard from both
of you upwards of an hour,

40:07.171 --> 40:09.349
you want to forever try the
case to make the plaintiff

40:09.373 --> 40:10.917
suffer, and you

40:10.941 --> 40:13.061
want to catch them with their
pants down so they can't

40:13.085 --> 40:14.755
prepare properly.

40:14.779 --> 40:17.624
Both positions strategically
valid, both positions

40:17.648 --> 40:18.992
logically flawed.

40:19.016 --> 40:22.229
Gentlemen, you have 30 days
to complete discovery.

40:22.253 --> 40:24.064
Trial begins in another 30 days,

40:24.088 --> 40:26.466
I'm sorry if you're client
has to miss his basketball

40:26.490 --> 40:30.237
season but my docket does not
revolve around basketball.

40:30.261 --> 40:32.021
And I'm sorry if you're
client has to work to

40:32.045 --> 40:34.574
prepare for trial but
sometimes counselor,

40:34.598 --> 40:36.877
that's the way it goes.

40:36.901 --> 40:38.636
Thank you, gentlemen.

40:39.537 --> 40:40.580
- Thank you your Honor.

40:40.604 --> 40:41.481
- Thank you your Honor.

40:41.505 --> 40:42.907
- You're welcome.

40:58.322 --> 41:00.267
- I had hoped you'd be a
little more sympathetic

41:00.291 --> 41:02.893
to my client's case your Honor.

41:03.828 --> 41:07.174
- I am a man of both fact
and faith Mr. Brown,

41:07.198 --> 41:09.709
and I would suggest you
find a strong dose of both

41:09.733 --> 41:11.836
before this trial begins.

41:32.957 --> 41:35.135
- I'm Joseph T.
Herrington, trial lawyer,

41:35.159 --> 41:37.804
Judge Rogers asked that I,

41:37.828 --> 41:40.740
that we intervene and bring
our two hundred years

41:40.764 --> 41:43.043
of collective
experience to bare.

41:43.067 --> 41:45.469
Now who is this lawyer who is

41:46.837 --> 41:49.406
shaking a stick in the beehive.

41:53.177 --> 41:54.688
Smart, filed a

41:54.712 --> 41:57.290
claim for retaliation.

41:57.314 --> 42:01.261
Doesn't depend on the success
of the underlying claim.

42:01.285 --> 42:02.353
Nevertheless.

42:13.264 --> 42:15.942
Michael Brown, Yale Law in 1985,

42:15.966 --> 42:19.513
three disciplinary complaints,
suspended for six months,

42:19.537 --> 42:21.748
last chance reinstatement.

42:21.772 --> 42:23.550
Misses deadlines.

42:23.574 --> 42:27.520
Last five years filed
65 cases, 58 settle,

42:27.544 --> 42:29.322
three lost at trial,

42:29.346 --> 42:33.017
two dismissed due to
lack of prosecution and

42:33.851 --> 42:36.930
one little victory for a
rear end car accident,

42:36.954 --> 42:37.955
verdict, uh,

42:40.190 --> 42:41.190
$2,500

42:44.161 --> 42:47.474
We will not simply
scorch the earth,

42:47.498 --> 42:50.610
they'll be no settlement,
they'll be no compromise,

42:50.634 --> 42:52.469
they'll be no way out.

42:53.470 --> 42:54.470
Still,

42:55.773 --> 42:57.784
you go get me a

42:57.808 --> 43:00.353
settlement conference with Mr.

43:00.377 --> 43:01.545
Michael Brown.

43:11.789 --> 43:12.856
- Aiden Paul?

43:16.293 --> 43:17.293
Aiden?

43:33.177 --> 43:35.257
- The first amendment does
not give coaches the right

43:35.281 --> 43:37.657
to impose their religion
on their students either.

43:37.681 --> 43:39.592
Coaches are
government employees,

43:39.616 --> 43:42.095
when they are coaching, they
are bound by the establishment

43:42.119 --> 43:44.097
clause of the first amendment.

43:44.121 --> 43:47.000
This means that they cannot
encourage, organize,

43:47.024 --> 43:48.702
or participate in prayer.

43:48.726 --> 43:50.670
When they get home,
they can pray,

43:50.694 --> 43:54.865
but whenever they coach,
they coach and not preach.

43:57.835 --> 44:00.947
- You know, you've managed
to divide the community

44:00.971 --> 44:02.682
in a way I haven't
seen I a while.

44:02.706 --> 44:05.919
Your resume is impressive
but I must say,

44:05.943 --> 44:07.854
and I'm not one to
beat around the bush,

44:07.878 --> 44:11.782
there is no one in the
state who will hire you.

44:17.788 --> 44:19.857
- Aiden Paul?

44:21.135 --> 44:22.135
- Good afternoon.

44:22.159 --> 44:24.604
- How may I help you?

44:24.628 --> 44:27.741
- This is my first time here,
so I don't really know what

44:27.765 --> 44:31.945
to do but I have to apply
for unemployment benefits.

44:31.969 --> 44:34.914
- Fill out these forms and
wait over there. Next.

44:34.938 --> 44:37.984
- Ma'am, I'm sorry I'm not
trying to violate any thing,

44:38.008 --> 44:42.179
but I've just been waiting
in line for three hours.

44:46.683 --> 44:48.118
- Denied.

44:55.025 --> 44:56.627
- You lost Michael.

44:58.328 --> 45:00.330
Don't let this escalate.

45:03.067 --> 45:06.379
It won't be good
for either of us.

45:06.403 --> 45:08.238
- I'll have the money.

45:09.406 --> 45:11.751
Long before it's due.

45:11.775 --> 45:12.775
Guaranteed.

45:43.507 --> 45:44.507
- Hi.

45:45.709 --> 45:47.220
- Hey.

45:47.244 --> 45:49.155
I've been looking for
you for over a week.

45:49.179 --> 45:50.523
Trial's around the corner,

45:50.547 --> 45:53.193
I'm meeting with the defense
in less than 24 hours.

45:53.217 --> 45:54.094
- I've been busy.

45:54.118 --> 45:55.361
- Your phones off.

45:55.385 --> 45:57.105
- I'm staying at a
friend's house right now.

45:57.129 --> 45:59.898
And I don't need
that extra bill.

46:00.924 --> 46:03.870
- Well good news and
bad, which first?

46:03.894 --> 46:05.305
- Um,

46:05.329 --> 46:06.372
I don't know why don't we
let the good news drown out

46:06.396 --> 46:08.274
the bad news?

46:08.298 --> 46:09.743
- Alright bad.

46:09.767 --> 46:12.579
The firm of Herrington Smith
and Hail took over the case.

46:12.603 --> 46:15.748
We drew the partner Joseph
Herrington, he's tough.

46:15.772 --> 46:18.685
Hasn't lost a trial in 20 years.

46:18.709 --> 46:20.620
- So we can't win?

46:20.644 --> 46:22.722
- Oh yeah, yeah we can beat him.

46:22.746 --> 46:24.224
But we may not have to.

46:24.248 --> 46:25.458
That's the good news.

46:25.482 --> 46:28.719
They called, wanted
to talk settlement.

46:29.753 --> 46:31.464
- Well that's...

46:31.488 --> 46:33.433
That's a good thing, right?

46:33.457 --> 46:35.526
- Good? That's very good.

46:36.426 --> 46:38.805
- See I pushed for this
trial to come up fast,

46:38.829 --> 46:40.273
that put pressure on them,

46:40.297 --> 46:42.257
they don't want to put their
resources in this and

46:42.281 --> 46:44.878
know that it's bad PR so,

46:44.902 --> 46:47.671
they want me to
come by tomorrow.

46:48.805 --> 46:52.652
- Like a get my job back,
like very soon, good thing?

46:52.676 --> 46:55.555
- I told them if getting your
job back wasn't on the table

46:55.579 --> 46:56.923
we wouldn't talk.

46:56.947 --> 46:58.958
They said let's talk.

46:58.982 --> 47:01.251
It'll all be over tomorrow.

47:14.565 --> 47:16.910
- Sorry, after conferring
with my client we decline to

47:16.934 --> 47:18.101
make an offer.

47:25.242 --> 47:28.321
- You never had any
plans to settle.

47:28.345 --> 47:31.658
That's considered deception,
deceit, old fashioned lying.

47:31.682 --> 47:33.927
- I did no such thing, there's
always a possibility,

47:33.951 --> 47:37.497
albeit a lower than
slight chance, but

47:37.521 --> 47:39.189
anything's possible.

47:40.457 --> 47:41.457
- Well.

47:42.893 --> 47:46.539
If that's the way you
want to play it.

47:46.563 --> 47:49.709
- You're really not gonna
dismiss this suit are you?

47:49.733 --> 47:51.010
- I don't quit.

47:51.034 --> 47:53.413
- After you learn a few
things about your client,

47:53.437 --> 47:56.950
I'm sure that withdrawing
might be a smart move.

47:56.974 --> 48:00.978
- Patience prevents me
from folding prematurely.

48:02.546 --> 48:04.624
- I got to give you
a little credit.

48:04.648 --> 48:07.060
Realizing that if you argue
the merits that the actual

48:07.084 --> 48:11.097
constitutionality, the
prayer, you lose so instead,

48:11.121 --> 48:12.632
you plead retaliation.

48:12.656 --> 48:15.401
That may get you an A in
my common law class but

48:15.425 --> 48:19.372
in the end, these are
little consequence here.

48:19.396 --> 48:21.040
- That's presumptuous.

48:21.064 --> 48:22.499
- Provatic maybe.

48:23.867 --> 48:24.867
Reality is

48:25.669 --> 48:27.337
if you argue prayer,

48:28.939 --> 48:29.939
you lose.

48:32.442 --> 48:35.989
- I'll take that
under consideration.

48:36.013 --> 48:39.092
- You realize this trial
starts in two weeks?

48:39.116 --> 48:40.860
Per your request?

48:40.884 --> 48:43.129
- That's fine counselor.

48:43.153 --> 48:45.198
I wouldn't mind
hastening the headline,

48:45.222 --> 48:47.734
Joseph Herrington loses.

